===Verb===
{{en-verb}}
# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To [[complain]] [[peevishly]].
# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To talk [[loudly]] and persistently.
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[repeat]] on and on, usually loudly or in [[complaint]].
# {{lb|en|intransitive|rare}} To make an [[outcry]]; to [[clamor]].
#* {{quote-book|en|1951|[[w:Isaac Asimov|Isaac Asimov]]|[[w:Foundation (novel)|Foundation]]|edition=1974|publisher=[[w:Panther Books|Panther Books Ltd]]|part=V|chapter=“The Merchant Princes”, chapter 17|page=182|text=It was a ship, but a whale to the ''Dark Nebula''’s minnow; and on its side was the Spaceship-and-Sun of the Empire. Every alarm on the ship '''yammered''' hysterically.}}
